ID: LT_Starts playing ... seconds after ... is triggered
EN: Starts playing ... seconds after ... is triggered

ID: LT_Set Condition under which Trigger Becomes Valid
EN: Set Condition under which Trigger Becomes Valid

ID: LT_Becomes valid ... seconds after ... starts to play
EN: Becomes valid ... seconds after ... starts to play

ID: LT_Becomes valid ... seconds after ... is triggered
EN: Becomes valid ... seconds after ... is triggered

ID: LT_Repeat ... times with an interval of ... seconds
EN: Repeat ... times with an interval of ... seconds

ID: LT_Maintain the same angle with track
EN: Maintain the same angle with track

ID: LT_Do you want to delete all objects?
EN: Do you want to delete all objects?
CN: 您确定要删除所有物体吗？

ID: LT_Gravity (All blocks and models will fall.)
EN: Gravity (All blocks and models will fall.)
CN: 有重力（所有砖和模型会有重力、会下落）

ID: LT_Magnetics (Blocks and models are automatically attracted and aligned when they are placed close enough.)
EN: Magnetics (Blocks and models are automatically attracted and aligned when they are placed close enough.)
CN: 有磁吸（砖或模型靠近时产生磁吸、对齐）

ID: LT_Orthogonal Correction (Blocks and models are automatically aligned along the x, y and z axes.)
EN: Orthogonal Correction (Blocks and models are automatically aligned along the x, y and z axes.)
CN: 正交校正（砖和模型与x、y、z轴自动对齐）

ID: LT_Scaling (Allow models to scale up or down)
EN: Scaling (Allow models to scale up or down)
CN: 缩放（支持与模型的缩放）

ID: LT_Scaling Projection (Objects can be modified out of the reach of controller.)
EN: Scaling Projection (Objects can be modified out of the reach of controller.)
CN: 缩放投影（可超过手柄触及范围）

ID: LT_Collision (Player is not allowed to go through concrete objects like a wall and a block.)
EN: Collision (Player is not allowed to go through concrete objects like a wall and a block.)
CN: 玩家碰撞（用户不能穿过墙、砖等有型物体）

ID: LT_The publishing process has begun. Since the process can take some time, the system will send you a notification once the process is complete.
EN: The publishing process has begun. Since the process can take some time, the system will send you a notification once the process is complete.
CN: 开始发布，发布过程由于上传资源将持续一段时间,发布完成后系统将使用消息队列通知您。
